Feature: Admin manage recipes
  Admin can create new recipes or edit
  And has the ability to create new tags
  Admin has access to user and collaborator list
  And see their information and recipes list
  And have the ability to edit the collaborator's recipes
  When a collaborator request to create a recipe
  Admin has the ability to accept or deny it

  Background: As a logged Admin

  Scenario: I should be able to create a new recipe

  Scenario: I should be able to edit a recipe

  Scenario: I should be able to create a new tag

  Scenario: I should be able to edit a recipe

  Scenario: I should see all registered users

  Scenario: I should see all collaborators

  Scenario: I have access to a collaborator recipes list

  Scenario: I have the ability to accept a collaborator request to create a recipe

  Scenario: I have the ability to deny a collaborator request to create a recipe

  Scenario: I should be able to see a list with all the recipes

  Scenario: I should be able to filter the recipes by a tag

  Scenario: I should be able to filter the recipes by multi tag
